steps.html_instructions: Head northwest on Bahriye Üçok Cd. toward Cumhuriyet Cd.
Miralay Şükrü Bey Cd. turns slightly left and becomes Zeytin Sk.

At the roundabout, take the 1st exit onto Erzurum Artvin Yolu/D950
Continue to follow D950
Keep left to stay on 50. Yıl Cd.
At the roundabout, take the 3rd exit onto Hastaneler Cd.
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Yenişehir Cd.

Continue onto Refik Saydam Cd./D950
Continue to follow D950

Keep right to continue on Cumhuriyet Cd./Erzurum Bingöl Yolu/D950
Continue to follow Erzurum Bingöl Yolu/D950

Turn right onto Bingöl Muş Yolu/D300
Continue to follow D300

At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Elazığ Bingöl Yolu/D300
Continue to follow D300

Keep left at the fork and merge onto Elazığ Malatya Yolu/D300
Continue to follow D300

Keep left to continue on Çevre Yolu Cd./D300
Destination will be on the left
